leads.lead_text: Petals entire or minutely crenate; leaves mostly 3–7 cm long, hairy on lower surface when mature, domatia absent; fruit blackish
Petals fringed or deeply lobed; leaves mostly 5–13 cm long, more or less glabrous on both surfaces when mature, domatia present; fruit blue
